{"tid":1750464,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"重要！今晚去監票既手足，一定要和平！","createTime":"2019-11-24T11:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T13:18:38.000Z","uid":5549,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2e1c7183dea879b7006481b8851f49ee1c9341e3","tid":1750464,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T11:54:54.000Z","msg":"保持克制，就算比藍絲撩都唔好郁手！<br />\n唔好比藉口比政府取消票站！"},{"pid":"1c2aaecf91deda6d17d9c8589f191970fb5b0813","tid":1750464,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:01:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d06d5f74b7a07d26c0c163f5362b6bd98ef46b2e","tid":1750464,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:02:25.000Z","msg":"10點半先開始<br />\n有排點<br />\n可以恰吓先落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e72e360e26cbc90853d7562274cfbc7d6fbb792c","tid":1750464,"uid":5549,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d06d5f74b7a07d26c0c163f5362b6bd98ef46b2e","tid":1750464,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:02:25.000Z","msg":"10點半先開始<br />\n有排點<br />\n可以恰吓先落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:09:47.000Z","msg":"帶定notebook落去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604f0a07e0c90e582f46ac03d3ea83c6f10524f6","tid":1750464,"uid":244357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:41:56.000Z","msg":"呢個投票率要預幾耐?要唔要拎張櫈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2f2083597a9cbc67b3b1dc0700147c1f326a41","tid":1750464,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"604f0a07e0c90e582f46ac03d3ea83c6f10524f6","tid":1750464,"uid":244357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:41:56.000Z","msg":"呢個投票率要預幾耐?要唔要拎張櫈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:43:11.000Z","msg":"最好啦，企到腳軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a136dd880c0375179bf76e3c1f32aea236f4c4a8","tid":1750464,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:52:09.000Z","msg":"【區議會選舉2015】真實案例<br />\n<br />\n<ins>第一單</ins><br />\n耀安選區初步點票出現大量問題票<br />\n沙田區耀安選區，經初步點票後出現高達757張問題票。據現場消息指，<span style=\"color: red;\">有不少選票上蓋印與一般剔號印章的形狀有異，懷疑印章出現問題</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>另一單</ins><br />\n2015年馬鞍山頌安陳震夏中學點票站，發生遺失選票箱鎖匙事件。凌晨零時，該點票站原定對4個票箱進行點票程序，<span style=\"color: red;\">惟發現其中一個票箱的鎖匙遺失了</span>，票箱打不開，票站主任向上級請示，獲律政司指示可以用工具將鎖頭撬開，職員決定用鐵鎚將票箱鎖頭鑿開，並會<span style=\"color: red;\">連同其餘選票一併點算</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>再另一單</ins><br />\n2015年石籬南選區點票出錯，多出一千張選票，足以左右選舉結果。<br />\n<br />\n葵青石籬南選區候選人梁國華表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">點票前選舉主任公佈當日全日累積有7182張選票，惟封箱之後，票站工作人員發現實際票站全日只發出6182張選票</span>，估計每一個投票時段的票數皆有錯漏，造成累積選票誤報1000張選票。<span style=\"color: red;\">梁國華表示當時向票站主任要求封箱</span>，將發出的選票與石籬南的選民登記名冊作比對，並延請選舉委員會及候選人的法律顧問核實結果。<span style=\"color: red;\">惟票站主任拒絕</span>，稱此做法為程序之外。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以大家一定要去監票！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"928ad01d1e12a89afaa71b8796264d52564ec04d","tid":1750464,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"604f0a07e0c90e582f46ac03d3ea83c6f10524f6","tid":1750464,"uid":244357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:41:56.000Z","msg":"呢個投票率要預幾耐?要唔要拎張櫈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:06:23.000Z","msg":"3個鐘走唔甩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7848c1f014f2ca5ff771e8643e55d366c27ca5b","tid":1750464,"uid":101906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:07:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ee112dbbc0779a9f87dae7138326949d62ce7c8","tid":1750464,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7848c1f014f2ca5ff771e8643e55d366c27ca5b","tid":1750464,"uid":101906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:07:01.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:18:38.000Z","msg":"thx"}]}